Kaitorisenkou's License Core
Version 1.00  (Last update: 2025-05-03)

- In this license, "Authorized Users" refers only to those who obtained or downloaded the product from the distribution sources designated by the developer.

- The following actions are permitted for "Authorized Users" of this product:
  - Personal use
  - Creation of derivative works (e.g., software, videos, images, written content, etc.)
  - Bug reports and feedback to the developer

- Bug reports and feedback will only be accepted through the channels specified in the README or description.

- Regardless of whether a user is authorized or not, the following actions are prohibited:
  - Redistribution of this product, in whole or in part, without meaningful modification or original contribution
  - Any illegal or malicious acts that cause or intend to cause harm to the developer's financial interests, mental or physical health, or reputation of the developer

- Regardless of authorization status, if a user violates applicable laws, the user assumes full responsibility.

- This product is provided "as is" without any warranties, express or implied. The developer shall not be liable for any damage to devices, software, peripherals, or data resulting from the use of this product.

- Any disputes arising in connection with this product shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts located in the developer’s country of residence (currently Japan), in the first instance.

- This license may be updated. The most current version of this license shall always apply.


ModularWeapons2 Specific License Definitions
Version 1.00  (Last update: 2025-05-03)

- This document provides supplementary definitions for the application of Kaitorisenkou's License Core (hereinafter "KLC") to this product.

- This document and KLC are collectively referred to as "the Licenses".

- For purposes of the Licenses, "Product" refers to ModularWeapons2, a Rimworld mod developed by Kaitorisenkou.

- This product incorporates or depends on the following third-party products, and is subject to their licenses or EULAs.  
  In the event of any conflict with this license, the following licenses shall take precedence:
  * RimWorld (Ludeon Studio)

- The distribution sources of this product specified by the developer are as follows:
  - Github (https://github.com/kaitorisenkou/ModularWeapons2/releases)
  - Steam Workshop (planned)

- This document may be updated. The most current version of this license shall always apply.


## In a nutshell...
- Don't be a bad guy
- Download from official sources
- As long as you follow these rules, you're free to use this and even make new stuff
- If the licenses gets updated, make sure to check back
